
    <html xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" 
          xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" 
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40">
    <head>
        <title>Project Development - User Acceptance Testing (UAT)</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #2d2724;
                background-color: #faf6eb;
                margin: 20px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                color: #c05c46;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #2d2724;
                padding-bottom: 5px;
            }
            h2, h3, h4 {
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                color: #2d2724;
            }
            table {
                width: 100%;
                border-collapse: collapse;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
            th, td {
                border: 2px solid #2d2724;
                padding: 10px;
                text-align: left;
            }
            th {
                background-color: #dda15e;
                color: #2d2724;
                font-weight: bold;
            }
            .meta-table {
                width: 50%;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }
            .meta-table th {
                background-color: #2d2724;
                color: #faf6eb;
            }
            .highlight {
                background-color: #faf6eb;
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                padding: 2px 5px;
                border: 1px solid #2d2724;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Project Development - User Acceptance Testing (UAT)</h1>
        <table class="meta-table">
            <tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Value</th></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Date</b></td><td>11 July 2026</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Team ID</b></td><td>TEAM-MERN-03</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Project Name</b></td><td>ShopEZ - Vintage Sepia Neubrutalist E-Commerce Platform</td></tr>
        </table>
        
    <h2>UAT Plan & Test Cases</h2>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>Test Case ID</th>
            <th>Scenario</th>
            <th>Steps to Execute</th>
            <th>Expected Outcome</th>
            <th>Status</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>TC-001</b></td>
            <td>User Authentication login</td>
            <td>1. Navigate to `/login`<br>2. Fill in seeded details.<br>3. Submit.</td>
            <td>Successful redirect to home; token set in local storage.</td>
            <td><span style="color: green; font-weight: bold;">PASS</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>TC-002</b></td>
            <td>Catalog Filtering</td>
            <td>1. Set price filter to max 4000.<br>2. Select Gaming category.</td>
            <td>Catalog updates in real-time to show Ares Pro Controller.</td>
            <td><span style="color: green; font-weight: bold;">PASS</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>TC-003</b></td>
            <td>Flipping Card Payment</td>
            <td>1. Proceed to checkout.<br>2. Choose Credit Card.<br>3. Click CVV field.</td>
            <td>Card widget performs 3D Y-axis flip to show back strip and signature box.</td>
            <td><span style="color: green; font-weight: bold;">PASS</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>TC-004</b></td>
            <td>Authorization Console</td>
            <td>1. Fill card details.<br>2. Submit pay order.</td>
            <td>Shows retro terminal logs processing payment steps, clearing bag, and redirecting.</td>
            <td><span style="color: green; font-weight: bold;">PASS</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>TC-005</b></td>
            <td>Stale Auth Interceptor</td>
            <td>1. Open app with stale database token.<br>2. Attempt Checkout.</td>
            <td>Axios intercepts 401, triggers logout, and redirects to `/login`.</td>
            <td><span style="color: green; font-weight: bold;">PASS</span></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    </body>
    </html>
    